[{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1263","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1263.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1399","title":"SGI IRIX 6.2 SpaceWare spaceball 本地权限提升漏洞","description":"SGI IRIX 6.2 系统自带的 SpaceWare 7.3 v1.0 中的 spaceball 程序存在本地权限提升漏洞。该程序在处理 HOSTNAME 环境变量时未进行充分验证，攻击者可构造包含 shell 命令的 HOSTNAME 环境变量值，使 spaceball 程序以 root 权限执行任意命令，最终获得系统的 root 权限。此漏洞仅需本地访问权限即可利用，影响运行受影响版本 IRIX 6.2 并安装了 SpaceWare 的系统。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.2,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1399"],"sources":["cve","exploitdb"],"published":"1997-08-20","updated":"2024-11-20","remediation":"删除 SpaceWare 程序，或在 $SWDIR/spaceball.sh 的 Utilities 部分将 HOSTNAME 设置为 /usr/bsd/hostname，以防止环境变量注入导致的命令执行。建议联系 SGI 获取安全补丁。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-18T08:21:14Z","references":["https://nvd.nist.gov/vuln/detail/CVE-1999-1399","http://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=87602746719552&w=2","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/471"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":["http://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=87602746719552&w=2","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/471"],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1263.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1425","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1425.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1250","title":"Blue World Lasso CGI 任意文件读取漏洞","description":"Blue World 公司开发的 Lasso 应用中的 CGI 程序存在任意文件读取漏洞，该 CGI 程序运行于 WebSTAR 及其他 Web 服务器上时，未对用户提交的文件路径参数进行充分过滤与验证。远程未经认证的攻击者可通过构造包含路径遍历序列的特制 HTTP 请求，读取服务器上任意文件，导致敏感信息泄露。CVSS 评分 5.0，危害等级中等。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1250"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1997-08-19T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:50:02.273","remediation":"升级 Lasso 至 8.0 及以上版本，该 CGI 接口在后续版本中已重构并修复了路径遍历问题。如无法升级，在 Web 服务器层面限制对 Lasso CGI 脚本的访问权限，仅允许授权 IP 调用，并禁用目录遍历相关的 URL 参数传递功能。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-20T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.securityfocus.com/archive/1/7506","https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/2044","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/e25ede9c3545efaa8ff0b393e30e48edb07502a8/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1250.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1250","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/1fe9b156eeeb72b8f8baa50bbe7bc0d9806e8c64/content/CVE-1999-1250.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/248c2167e720df96125f6ac9925793063a207510/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-1250.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/cdfc8886d71af7ef3bdab3e4db46753ff8af6538/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-5pj2-qf29-pjw9/GHSA-5pj2-qf29-pjw9.json","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x88000/87798/info.html","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/63d4031680b3d3fa77b826660a1e30ffc70ff5cd/nvdcve/CVE-1999-1250.json","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_154400_154500.json","https://github.com/Ethishh/securin_assessment/blob/e6ce9197b6593ae46f3f5646d268181eea6cbb31/cve_sync.log","https://github.com/Vasileios-Mavroeidis/semantic-stix-vulnerability/blob/30f07606133364b9623f401bc306c8c9cbcf9386/vulnerability/vulnerability--b00175c9-574a-404f-a5ec-1e76ff6df8f2.owl"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1425.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0081","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0081.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0024","title":"ISC BIND DNS 查询标识符可预测导致缓存投毒漏洞","description":"BIND DNS 服务器存在 DNS 缓存投毒漏洞，由于使用可预测的查询 ID 作为事务标识符，远程攻击者可通过向目标 DNS 服务器发送伪造的 DNS 响应报文，在无需认证的情况下实施缓存投毒攻击，将合法域名解析指向恶意 IP 地址，导致用户被重定向至恶意网站或遭受中间人攻击。该漏洞影响早期 BIND 版本，CVSS 评分 5.0，危害等级中等。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0024"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1997-08-13T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:47:22.577","remediation":"升级 BIND 至 4.9.7 或 8.2 及以上版本，该版本引入了随机化 DNS 查询 ID 机制，防止攻击者预测 ID 实施缓存投毒。若无法升级，可在 named.conf 中限制递归查询仅对受信任内部网段开放（allow-recursion），并在边界防火墙上阻断 UDP 53 端口的非授权外部访问作为临时缓解。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0024"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0081.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0314","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0314.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0152","title":"Data General DG/UX finger 远程命令执行漏洞","description":"DG/UX 系统的 finger 服务程序存在命令注入漏洞，远程攻击者无需身份认证即可通过向目标 finger 服务发送包含 shell 元字符（如分号、管道符等）的特制请求，利用服务程序对用户输入过滤不严的缺陷，在目标系统上以 finger 进程权限执行任意命令。该漏洞影响 DG/UX 操作系统，CVSS 评分 7.5，危害等级高，攻击复杂度低，利用方式简单，影响较为广泛。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0152"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1997-08-11T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:47:42.707","remediation":"立即禁用 finger 服务（/etc/inetd.conf 中注释 finger 行并重启 inetd），或在防火墙层面阻止外部对 finger 端口（79/tcp）的访问。由于 DG/UX 已停止技术支持且无官方补丁，建议迁移至受支持的现代操作系统以彻底消除风险。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0152"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0314.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1432","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1432.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1262","title":"{\"_meta\":{},\"stopReason\":\"end_turn\",\"usage\":{\"cachedReadTokens\":1728,\"inputTokens\":9067,\"outputTokens\":20,\"totalTokens\":10815}}","description":"Netscape 4.5 中的 Java 实现存在授权绕过漏洞，Java Applet 未正确限制只能连接加载其来源的主机，而是允许连接到任意远程主机，违反了 Java 沙箱安全模型。远程攻击者可诱使用户访问恶意网页，触发该漏洞执行未授权操作，如扫描内部网络或发起网络请求。该漏洞 CVSS 评分 5.1，危害等级中危，影响 Netscape 4.5 及可能的相关版本。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.1,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1262"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1997-08-01T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:50:03.807","remediation":"升级到 Netscape Navigator 4.51 或更高版本以修复 Java 小程序跨主机连接的授权缺陷；如无法立即升级，可在浏览器中禁用 Java 或在防火墙层面禁止浏览器进程向非源主机发起出站连接作为临时缓解措施。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-20T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.securityfocus.com/archive/1/12231","https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/1727","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/d00c4bdddf18e05c46df568e8ae91e7912ce321c/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1262.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1262","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/1fe9b156eeeb72b8f8baa50bbe7bc0d9806e8c64/content/CVE-1999-1262.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/24512263eb77d6af2cecd67bd2460f761fc94bea/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-1262.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/cdfc8886d71af7ef3bdab3e4db46753ff8af6538/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-2ccq-2xr5-3q62/GHSA-2ccq-2xr5-3q62.json","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-1262.json","https://github.com/leego972/titanai/blob/afa5b2310463aae5781d3fd9408071bf38e79806/data/raw/corpus_D_cyber/nvd_cve_000199.txt","https://github.com/oasis-open/cti-stix-common-objects/blob/55ba7598cbd5a52577b6887871505d931d85cb61/objects/vulnerability/vulnerability--5fd09560-4a3b-4ba3-bc04-483a5e7b44bc.json","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x88000/87854/info.html","https://github.com/Christopher0129/security-knowledge-base/blob/ecec748afe5bbe2fcd2fd04b00fb46bc827b2c5d/system-vulnerabilities/macos.md"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1432.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0781","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0781.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0524","title":"Linux Kernel 远程主机 ICMP 信息泄露漏洞","description":"CVE-1999-0524 是 Linux 内核中 ICMP 协议实现存在的信息泄露缺陷。目标系统默认允许任意远程主机向其发送 ICMP 掩码请求（Type 17/18）与 ICMP 时间戳请求（Type 13/14），并在未做来源限制的情况下返回本机的子网掩码、当前时间戳及发送时间戳等网络配置信息。攻击者在无需身份认证的条件下，只需向目标主机发送特制的 ICMP 请求报文即可获取上述信息，从而辅助推断目标网络拓扑、子网划分及系统时钟，为后续针对性攻击提供侦察依据。该漏洞影响启用了相关 ICMP 响应功能的 Linux 内核系统，虽属中危信息泄露，但在内网探测与隐蔽侦察场景中具有一定利用价值。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":4.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0524"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1997-08-01T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:34.703","remediation":"升级 Linux 内核至发行版提供的最新安全版本，并在 sysctl.conf 中设置 net.ipv4.icmp_echo_ignore_broadcasts=1 以禁用对广播地址的 ICMP 响应。同时通过 iptables 或 nftables 添加规则阻断外部主机发来的 ICMP timestamp 请求（类型 13）和 ICMP address mask 请求（类型 17），例如使用 iptables -A INPUT -p icmp --icmp-type timestamp-request -j DROP 和 iptables -A INPUT -p icmp --icmp-type address-mask-request -j DROP。如无法立即升级内核，可在防火墙层限制 ICMP 类型 13 和 17 的入站流量作为临时缓解。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["http://descriptions.securescout.com/tc/11010","http://descriptions.securescout.com/tc/11011","http://kb.juniper.net/InfoCenter/index?page=content&id=JSA10705","http://kb.vmware.com/selfservice/microsites/search.do?cmd=displayKC&externalId=1434","http://www.osvdb.org/95","https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/306","https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/322","https://kc.mcafee.com/corporate/index?page=content&id=SB10053","https://support.f5.com/csp/article/K15277","https://github.com/trickest/cve/blob/6e5939e8074723d33adaf5b2f8b0352edab9ba8d/1999/CVE-1999-0524.md","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/1ce36d0de2f3ddd1d56c222c398df994c8c331b1/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0524.json","https://github.com/ycdxsb/PocOrExp_in_Github/blob/0e18153fbb4123e7b766fcd8c28227fcde5a3816/1999/README.md","https://github.com/Indie365/cbl-mariner/blob/80d864c0a617439675510c037c8a4589aa596fbb/SPECS/kernel-hci/CVE-1999-0524.nopatch","https://github.com/fleetdm/fleet/blob/2d49b61ff5c6af212f5b41f22f2fb25deebaa4a6/server/vulnerabilities/nvd/cpe_matching_rules.go","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/f581b54f28a314b57ac171b83d3b2d21db7414a0/SSVC/data/1999/CVE-1999-0524.json","https://github.com/CVEProject/cve-reference-ingest-data/blob/cd275183e69131386d0c86c5a1716b6a67ff7687/references/CVE-1999-0524-2025-03-17-1422","https://github.com/openembedded/openembedded-core/blob/171af3b2915dd076c8d1b205ff75eac1ebd5a586/meta/conf/distro/include/cve-extra-exclusions.inc","https://github.com/openbmc/docs/blob/cf706722293b681fbcbb852eee05a9ae045ac635/security/network-security-considerations.md","https://github.com/0xMarcio/cve/blob/f24db61575bca326440113bfa8e6a6aa18028087/1999/CVE-1999-0524.md","https://github.com/noraj/ChronoLeak","https://github.com/threatlabindonesia/CVE-1999-0524-ICMP-Timestamp-and-Address-Mask-Request-Exploit","https://github.com/biontdv/CVE-1999-0524-POC","https://github.com/b1tsec/CVE-1999-0524","https://github.com/Ransc0rp1on/ICMP-Timestamp-POC"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0781.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0423","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0423.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0238","title":"PHP PHP/fi 2.0 目录遍历漏洞","description":"PHP/FI 2.0 的 php.cgi 脚本存在目录遍历漏洞，远程攻击者可通过向目标系统发送特制的 HTTP 请求，利用路径遍历技术读取服务器上的任意文件，包括敏感配置文件、密码文件等。该漏洞影响 PHP/FI 2.0 版本，攻击者无需认证即可利用，危害较大。","severity":"CRITICAL","score":10.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0238"],"sources":["exploitdb"],"published":"1997-08-01T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:47:58.650","remediation":"立即移除或禁用 PHP/fi 2.0 中的 php.cgi 脚本，升级至 PHP 3.0 或更高版本（PHP 3.0 起已重写架构并修复此目录遍历问题）。如无法升级，在 Web 服务器配置中限制 php.cgi 仅访问指定目录，或通过 .htaccess / httpd.conf 禁止直接访问该脚本。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0238","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/20567","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/ead50dc12e50bdd7f50b53d9d01c9f9946862c44/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0238.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0238","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/45be3b4afd9c4397ee32a5cbf6819a590220b0c1/content/CVE-1999-0238.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/4ed191c1149de50e461e9a357f4a3a22e603f0d1/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0238.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/b7a93df7f7051799495805bc211adea8d202dae7/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-r5ff-p26w-7pfj/GHSA-r5ff-p26w-7pfj.json","https://github.com/marcellodesales/aibbp-reverse-engineer/blob/960f610d597aae9fec1cc5f03c68679be00c222d/reverse_engineer/invicti/vulnerabilities/db/vulnerabilities/vdb/1999/0xxx/cve-1999-0238.yaml","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-0238.json","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x3000/2250/info.html","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/pocs/1999/POC-AVE-1999-0423.toml"],"repo_exp_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/exploits/1999/EXP-AVE-1999-0423.toml"],"has_poc":true,"has_exp":true,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0423.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0829","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0829.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0566","title":"IBM AIX syslog 文件写入拒绝服务漏洞","description":"攻击者可以从任意位置向 syslog 文件写入数据，通过填满日志磁盘空间导致拒绝服务，同时可掩盖攻击行为。该漏洞影响 IBM AIX 系统，无需身份认证即可远程利用。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0566"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1997-08-01","updated":"2024-06-16","remediation":"限制 syslog 文件的写入权限，配置日志轮转策略，部署入侵检测系统监控异常日志写入行为。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2024-06-16T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0566"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0829.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0498","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0498.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0301","title":"SunOS/Solaris ps 命令缓冲区溢出漏洞","description":"SunOS 和 Solaris 系统中的 ps 命令存在缓冲区溢出漏洞。本地攻击者可通过向 ps 命令传递特制参数触发缓冲区溢出，从而获取 root 权限，实现完全控制目标系统。该漏洞影响 SunOS 5.3/5.4/5.5/5.5.1 及 Solaris 2.3/2.4/2.5/2.5.1 等多个版本。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.2,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0301"],"sources":["cve","exploitdb"],"published":"1997-08-01","updated":"2026-06-16","remediation":"建议升级到不受影响的 SunOS/Solaris 版本，或安装 Sun 安全公告 149 号提供的补丁程序。限制本地用户对 ps 命令的访问权限可缓解风险。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T12:06:30.705882439+00:00","references":["http://sunsolve.sun.com/pub-cgi/retrieve.pl?doctype=coll&doc=secbull/149"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0498.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1470","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1470.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1308","title":"HP HP-UX 本地权限提升漏洞","description":"HP-UX 10.20 系统中某些程序未能正确处理超过 60000 的大用户 ID（UID）或组 ID（GID），存在本地权限提升漏洞。本地攻击者可通过创建特制的大 UID/GID 账户，利用该缺陷绕过权限检查机制，从而获取更高系统权限。该漏洞影响 HP-UX 10.20 版本，攻击者需拥有本地账户才能利用，CVSS 评分 4.6，危害等级中危。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":4.6,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1308"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1997-07-31T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:50:09.887","remediation":"升级 HP-UX 系统至 11.0 或更高版本，该问题已在后续版本中修复。如无法升级，请安装 HP 针对此漏洞发布的安全补丁（如 PHKL_19036 等补丁包），并在 /etc/default/security 中限制 UID/GID 最大值为 60000 以内，同时审查拥有超大 UID 的本地用户账户权限。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-20T00:00:00Z","references":["http://ciac.llnl.gov/ciac/bulletins/h-09.shtml","http://ciac.llnl.gov/ciac/bulletins/h-91.shtml","http://www.iss.net/security_center/static/7594.php","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/4e8d44fc9434dcaf08511a3267e0bf049a6756de/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1308.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1308","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/470a5f1c0d1bd36cd0a6327cda49cf96a1474588/content/CVE-1999-1308.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/f9199c6ea2112c9d2536a126688b640a45f0982a/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-1308.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/4544d3857250fe21711ce8febf38e8822729678f/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-6h2j-2p74-3pmh/GHSA-6h2j-2p74-3pmh.json","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x88000/87891/info.html","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_154400_154500.json","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/39f1db26eec9899ab2f8110ab3b45424c6fe9ec2/nvdcve/CVE-1999-1308.json","https://github.com/leego972/titanai/blob/afa5b2310463aae5781d3fd9408071bf38e79806/data/raw/corpus_D_cyber/nvd_cve_000197.txt","https://github.com/oasis-open/cti-stix-common-objects/blob/55ba7598cbd5a52577b6887871505d931d85cb61/objects/vulnerability/vulnerability--5614f315-b32d-4cfc-a30a-254d324597b4.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1470.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1407","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1407.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1217","title":"Microsoft Windows NT PATH 本地权限提升漏洞","description":"Windows NT 系统默认将当前工作目录（.）包含在 PATH 环境变量中，导致命令解析时先搜索当前目录再搜索系统目录。本地低权限用户可在任意目录中放置与常用系统命令同名的木马程序（例如 ftp.exe、net.exe），当管理员或高权限用户切换到该目录并执行对应命令时，木马程序将优先被加载执行，从而劫持权限并实现本地提权。攻击条件为攻击者具备本地登录权限且能在目标系统磁盘上创建文件，无需网络访问即可完成利用。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":4.6,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1217"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1997-07-25","updated":"2026-06-16","remediation":"编辑系统环境变量，将 PATH 中单独的 \".\" 条目彻底移除；确保 %SystemRoot% 及 %SystemRoot%\\System32 等系统目录始终排在用户目录之前，系统命令执行时不再搜索当前工作目录；通过组策略限制普通用户写入系统关键目录的权限，并对本地登录账户实施最小权限原则。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-19T00:00:00Z","references":["http://marc.info/?l=ntbugtraq&m=87602726319426&w=2","http://marc.info/?l=ntbugtraq&m=87602726319435&w=2","https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/526"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1407.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1317","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1317.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1068","title":"Oracle HTTP Server 2.1 PL/SQL 存储过程远程拒绝服务漏洞","description":"Oracle WebServer 2.1 在处理 PL/SQL 存储过程时存在输入验证缺陷，远程攻击者无需身份认证即可向目标服务器发送超长 HTTP GET 请求，触发服务进程崩溃或资源耗尽，导致拒绝服务。该漏洞影响 Oracle HTTP Server 2.1 版本，攻击复杂度低，危害等级中等。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1068"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1997-07-23T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:39.280","remediation":"升级到 Oracle HTTP Server（Oracle Webserver 的后续产品）或迁移至受支持的 Oracle WebLogic Server。如无法升级，在反向代理或 WAF 层面限制 HTTP GET 请求 URI 长度不超过 2048 字节，并过滤包含超长查询参数的请求。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-20T00:00:00Z","references":["http://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=87602661419366&w=2","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/7481e97cf7b60a5b982d99d7dad1ea61174940fb/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1068.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1068","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/1fe9b156eeeb72b8f8baa50bbe7bc0d9806e8c64/content/CVE-1999-1068.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/c1321b1a6b0cb3a4c18f791e2c8443742c0cb0b0/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-1068.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/cdfc8886d71af7ef3bdab3e4db46753ff8af6538/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-g6wg-27vg-grv9/GHSA-g6wg-27vg-grv9.json","https://github.com/marcellodesales/aibbp-reverse-engineer/blob/960f610d597aae9fec1cc5f03c68679be00c222d/reverse_engineer/invicti/vulnerabilities/db/vulnerabilities/vdb/1999/1xxx/cve-1999-1068.yaml","https://github.com/blackhook/nessus-plugins/blob/64177d96abbb07c58cf7e131046b067ebc61fcb5/O/ows_overflow.nasl","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-1068.json","https://github.com/leego972/titanai/blob/afa5b2310463aae5781d3fd9408071bf38e79806/data/raw/corpus_D_cyber/nvd_cve_000194.txt","https://github.com/hungryfoolou/Vulnerability_Mining/blob/3df1d8ed0489ae1228f975ae1f58a690aae53886/craw/cveid_craw/cveid_craw/data/cveid_by_kind/cveid_dos.txt"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/pocs/1999/POC-AVE-1999-1317.toml"],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":true,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1317.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1224","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1224.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0971","title":"Exim Buffer 1.6.2/1.6.51 缓冲区溢出（本地权限提升）漏洞","description":"Exim 邮件服务器 1.6.2 和 1.6.51 版本存在缓冲区溢出漏洞，本地攻击者可通过在 .forward 文件中构造过长的 :include: 选项触发溢出，从而提升权限至 root。该漏洞影响 Exim 特定版本，CVSS 评分 7.2，属高危本地提权漏洞，攻击需具备本地账户访问权限，利用方式为精心构造恶意 .forward 文件触发栈溢出执行任意代码。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.2,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0971"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1997-07-22T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:26.097","remediation":"升级 Exim 至 2.0.0 或更高版本，该版本已修复 :include: 选项的缓冲区边界检查。如无法升级，在 /etc/exim/exim.conf 中禁用 .forward 文件处理（设置 allow_forward = false），并限制本地用户对 .forward 文件的写入权限（chmod 644）。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-18T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.securityfocus.com/archive/1/7301","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/20333","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/e268305fd8644994d337819e469d1f89bafde833/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0971.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0971","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/5cf8ba64f356efe9269b21eca2f657231acd746c/content/CVE-1999-0971.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/76af88afbb282d6c9e8ce3b9f6942bcb7e39be57/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0971.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/d9ad03f9df46533ce9229f9da6bbf66bd77a3f4f/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-qxcj-688p-v8g5/GHSA-qxcj-688p-v8g5.json","https://github.com/mitre/cti/blob/ea1adfe1a68ca3dcfe2dd883180b8cf10a988824/capec/2.1/attack-pattern/attack-pattern--8e403d18-af4e-4abd-bd38-0f99f74b4636.json","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-0971.json","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt","https://github.com/andreafioraldi/ToolsForCyberChallenge/blob/197d3dfd204cf1b9d1af1451455c8831c3ff9948/generated/files_4.list.dict","https://github.com/leego972/titanai/blob/afa5b2310463aae5781d3fd9408071bf38e79806/data/raw/corpus_D_cyber/nvd_cve_000193.txt"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1224.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1256","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1256.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1208","title":"IBM AIX ping 缓冲区溢出漏洞","description":"IBM AIX 4.2 及早期版本中的 ping 命令存在栈缓冲区溢出漏洞，本地攻击者可通过向 ping 命令传递超长命令行参数触发栈溢出，覆盖返回地址并执行任意代码，从而获得 root 权限。该漏洞影响 AIX 4.2 及更早版本，攻击者需具备本地账户访问权限，通过构造超长参数调用 ping 即可触发缓冲区溢出实现本地提权至 root 权限，CVSS 评分 7.2，属高危本地提权漏洞。IBM 已发布补丁修复该漏洞。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.2,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1208"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1997-07-21T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:57.010","remediation":"建议将 IBM AIX 升级至 4.3 或更高版本（官方已在该版本中修复 ping 缓冲区溢出）。若暂无法升级，可通过应用 IBM 官方补丁（如 APAR IX84737 等对应修复包）并限制普通用户对 /usr/sbin/ping 的执行权限（移除 setuid 位或收紧文件权限）作为临时缓解措施，同时加强本地用户账户管理。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-19T00:00:00Z","references":["http://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=87602661419330&w=2","http://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=87602661419337&w=2","https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/803","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19307","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/7e65fa522cff0172990568230ff9b719b8650296/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1208.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1208","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/1fe9b156eeeb72b8f8baa50bbe7bc0d9806e8c64/content/CVE-1999-1208.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/7aedbd0209e609a1924ad29a8dda684737576137/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-1208.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/5d945305f2cad48b7bb06af582393a58c31555d3/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-h664-4mr2-whv6/GHSA-h664-4mr2-whv6.json","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x1000/387/info.html","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_154400_154500.json","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/63d4031680b3d3fa77b826660a1e30ffc70ff5cd/nvdcve/CVE-1999-1208.json","https://github.com/andreafioraldi/ToolsForCyberChallenge/blob/197d3dfd204cf1b9d1af1451455c8831c3ff9948/generated/files_2.list.dict","https://github.com/oasis-open/cti-stix-common-objects/blob/55ba7598cbd5a52577b6887871505d931d85cb61/objects/vulnerability/vulnerability--0feafa0f-ee74-450f-a0f6-2a3d06fac48b.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1256.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0432","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0432.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0247","title":"INN nnrpd 缓冲区溢出远程代码执行漏洞","description":"INN (InterNetNews) 新闻服务器中的 nnrpd 程序存在栈缓冲区溢出漏洞，版本 1.6 及之前版本受影响。远程攻击者无需身份认证即可向目标系统发送特制的新闻组请求，触发缓冲区溢出，从而在服务器上以 nnrpd 进程权限执行任意代码。该漏洞影响广泛部署的 INN 新闻服务器系统，CVSS 评分 7.5，危害等级高。建议升级至 INN 1.6 以上版本修复。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0247"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1997-07-21T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:47:59.740","remediation":"升级 INN 至 2.0 或更高版本，该漏洞在 INN 1.7 及后续版本中已被修复。如无法升级，可在 innd 配置中限制 nnrpd 服务的远程访问来源 IP，或禁用 nnrpd 的远程连接功能作为临时缓解措施。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.nai.com/nai_labs/asp_set/advisory/17_inn_avd.asp","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/1443","https://github.com/trickest/cve/blob/34851454a7b07498072de47d56f63daa4a4f524d/1999/CVE-1999-0247.md","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/ab6ab436962e16237b21ed9d4458dafc38c692fc/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0247.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0247","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/601a95d57be2a57306cd88389c2251f34b2fbcc1/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-0247.json","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/a55bddfc5dd568e972e08b703ab596ed3580b7ba/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0247.json","https://github.com/mabitoski/cve_submodules/blob/44ad7e2705b3aef1b2ffaf64bd47596c10a6c2e4/1999/CVE-1999-0247.md","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/49899a53e9c2e620c99e0234afe3c50e512ad851/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-69m7-6fwc-hxpx/GHSA-69m7-6fwc-hxpx.json","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/blackhook/nessus-plugins/blob/64177d96abbb07c58cf7e131046b067ebc61fcb5/I/inn.nasl","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github